  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized Phase III study to evaluate efficancy of weekly cisplatin or nedaplatin
      concurrent with Intensity-modulated radiation therapy in Nasopharyngeal Carcinoma (NPC).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
